data.description: Welcome to very own piece of paradise. This beautiful newer construction home has 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms with a little over 1800 SF of living space. This home features Granite counter tops and tile throughout the home and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom has a huge walk in closet and master bathroom with his and hers sinks. The large backyard gives you an empty canvass to build a pool and if you enjoy seeing the morning sunrise or evening sunset the large lanai allows you ample space to create your very own backyard oasis. Don't wait to schedule an appointment to see this beautiful home today.
